comments.body:
Currently, I test my app with some guild mates.
And API seem retrieve wrongs data.
In fact, they retrieve their chars and some others.

I test API key of one tester (direct in browser with url of API) and it return:
[“Barak De Cherek”,“Sahe Onirée”,“Morjah”,“Mahr Cell”,“Labbee”,“Nittsi”,“Chest Of Spaeda”]

In this list, Chest Of Spaeda is one of my chars and Nittsi belong to another guild mate.
By the way he can view datas of these chars.

We try with new generated API Key and we have same bug.

We wait 10 min and try again. All data are correct, it seem link to anet API server cache.
